did.abstract: Collection includes: Decisions, Releases, cases, fact-finding reports, Annual reports, impasse panel reports. Divided into 5 series: 1. Releases 2. Decisions from Board of Collective Bargaining. 3. Decisions from Board of Certification 4. Impasses Pane (or Arbitration Board) Decisions 5. Arbitration Cases
